{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "46b52613-2322-40ad-ba64-b3c068c861e1", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/46b52613-2322-40ad-ba64-b3c068c861e1@1.pkg/1772597698567/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699038", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/46b52613-2322-40ad-ba64-b3c068c861e1@1.pkg/1772597698567/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597699038"}, "identifier": "46b52613-2322-40ad-ba64-b3c068c861e1", "test_cases": "", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>本题考查构建和谐家庭的方法。</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>A：材料中并未提到友谊，&ldquo;以比赛让青少年理解友谊的竞争性&rdquo;与材料无关。因此A错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>B：亲子一同协作参与的家务劳动比赛有利于引导青少年体悟劳动中的亲情温暖。B符合题意，因此B正确</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>C：&ldquo;强化履行家庭责任的法定义务意识&rdquo;与材料中的比赛内容无关，故C错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>D：&ldquo;增强通过劳动获取物质回报的意识&rdquo;与材料主旨不相符合。因此D错误</b></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;\"><b>因此选B</b></span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": ""}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）九年级小杨同学最近很苦恼，中考填报志愿，他想选择自己喜欢的学校，父母则希望他选择离家近的学校。他不愿被父母干涉，但又特别希望获得父母的支持。针对小杨的苦恼，最恰当的建议是（　　）</span></p></div>", "label": "", "title": "（改编）九年级小杨同学最近很苦恼，中考填报志愿，他想选择自己喜欢的学校，父母则希望他选择离家近的学校。他不愿被父母干涉，但又特别希望获得父母的支持。针对小杨的苦恼，最恰当的建议是（　　）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {}, "time_dependent": false, "examples": {"responses": [], "feedbacks": [], "items": []}, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["A"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/46b52613-2322-40ad-ba64-b3c068c861e1@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754977961167", "lang": "", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "evaluate_result_show": false, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "subtype": "", "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options": [], "orientation": 0, "multiple": false, "raw": false, "titles": [], "rows": 1, "response_identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "0", "max_choices": 1, "gap_imgs": [], "shuffle": false, "choices": [{"identifier": "A", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>通过平等协商，寻求共同认可的方案</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "B", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>表面听从父母，填报志愿时坚持己见</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "C", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>完全拒绝沟通，坚持个人的自主选择</span></p></div>"}, {"identifier": "D", "correct": false, "match_max": 0, "group_id": "", "fixed": true, "text": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>顺从父母安排，维持家庭的表面和谐</span></p></div>"}], "prompt": "<div><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span>（改编）九年级小杨同学最近很苦恼，中考填报志愿，他想选择自己喜欢的学校，父母则希望他选择离家近的学校。他不愿被父母干涉，但又特别希望获得父母的支持。针对小杨的苦恼，最恰当的建议是（　　）</span></p></div>", "object": {"data": "", "width": "1000", "type": "image/png", "params": {"originalImage": "", "blankImage": ""}, "height": "600"}}], "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878"}, "source": {"container_id": "elearning-